Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface ConceptTypeAssertion

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Assertion, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, TypeAssertion
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConceptTypeAssertionImpl
    public interface ConceptTypeAssertion
extends TypeAssertion
    A representation of the model object 'Concept Type Assertion'. ConceptTypeAssertion is a type assertion specifying a type for a concept instance. It can be specified directly on an concept instance, or indirectly on a reference to one.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Owning Instance
    • Owning Reference
